    {
      "heading": "The Team",
      "subheading": null,
      "body": "Carina Lopez - Hair Designer\nYou can often find me at the gym, spending time with my family, or enjoying the beach.\n\nMakayla Davila - Hair Designer\nWhen I'm not behind the chair, you'll usually find me staying active—whether it's playing pickleball, exploring the coast, or spending quality time with my family.\n\nHope Sanchez - Hair Designer\nYou can find me lost in a good book (romance, horror, and thrillers) or binge-watching my favorite shows. All while sipping on some coffee.\n\nAmber Kehoe - Hair Designer\nOutside of the salon, I'm a proud mom of three (plus two amazing bonus kids!) and I love staying active with workouts that keep me energized.\n\nCat Barco - Owner & Hair Designer\nYou can usually find me sipping on a creamy protein coffee or, in the summer, a green tea lemonade with matcha—always with a podcast or audiobook playing in the background.",
